odern European languages. This was the name of the mother of John the Baptist (Luke 1:60). Etymologically, the name means ‘God is my oath’, and is therefore identical with <i>Elisheba</i>, the name of the wife of Aaron according to the genealogy at Exodus 6:23. The final element seems to have been altered by association with Hebrew <i>shabbāth</i> ‘Sabbath’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Elizabeth Prideaux was born in 1391, in Exeter, Devon, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with John Periam. She died in her hometown."},"et":{"1391–":"1391–Surnud","1388–Male":"1388–Surnud","1413–Male":"1413–Surnud","1391–Female":"1391–Surnud","1413":"1413","1388":"1388","1391":"1391","Exeter, Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Exeter, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1391–":"1391–Kuollut","1388–Male":"1388–Kuollut","1413–Male":"1413–Kuollut","1391–Female":"1391–Kuollut","1413":"1413","1388":"1388","1391":"1391","Exeter, Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Exeter, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1391–":"1391–Décédée","1388–Male":"1388–Décédé","1413–Male":"1413–Décédé","1391–Female":"1391–Décédée","1413":"1413","1388":"1388","1391":"1391","Exeter, Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Exeter, Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth Prideaux est née en 1391, à Exeter, Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec John Periam. Elle est décédée dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"1391–":"1391–Verstorben","1388–Male":"1388–Verstorben","1413–Male":"1413–Verstorben","1391–Female":"1391–Verstorben","1413":"1413","1388":"1388","1391":"1391","Exeter, Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Exeter, Devon, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth Prideaux wurde 1391 in Exeter, Devon, England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hatte mit John Periam mindestens 1 Sohn. Sie starb in ihrem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"1391–":"1391–Desede","1388–Male":"1388–Desede","1413–Male":"1413–Desede","1391–Female":"1391–Desede","1413":"1413","1388":"1388","1391":"1391","E